          "text": "Score ≤ 2\nLow risk (0-2.5%)\nConsider discharge home with close follow up\nScore 3-6\nIndeterminate risk\nConsider serial exams, consultation, or imaging\nScore ≥ 7\nHigh risk\nConsider surgical consultation",
